	  subtile task that are non ops.
	  
	  Added support for layers.

2008-02-15 16:04  robert

	* src/vpb/Destination.cpp: Changed the compute the of the grid
	  origin and xy interval to be done locally in doubles to fix
	  precision issues when working with high rest polygonal tiles

