	  src/vpb/DataSet.cpp, src/vpb/Destination.cpp, src/vpb/Source.cpp,
	  src/vpb/SpatialProperties.cpp, src/vpb/TaskFile.cpp: Improved
	  logging support, and introduced new TaskFile class for tracking
	  the
	  status of, running and stopping builds.

