	* Make/makedirdefs: From Brede Johansen, new OpenFlight plugin!!!!!
	  
	  By default the original flt plugin is still used, to select at
	  runtime
	  the new plugin set the env OSG_OPEN_FLIGHT_PLUGIN=new

