	* src/osgTerrain/DataSet.cpp: Changed the minimum tile image size
	  to be 4x4 to avoid problems in mipmap generation
	  that was occuring at sizes of 2x2, seemingly somewhere in the
	  OpenGL driver.

2005-10-25 13:28  robert

	* Make/makedirdefs: From Geoff Michel, added support for constrain
	  delaunay triangultion, and osgdelaunay example.

2005-10-13 08:05  robert

	* Make/dependencies, Make/makedirdefs: Added PRODUCER_INSTALLED=yes
	  make options to the unix build system, not defining
	  PRODUCER_INSTALLED=yes or setting it to another value than yes
	  (i.e no) will result
	  in the osgProducer library, OSG applications and demos not being
	  built.
	  
	  PRODUCER_INSTALLED=yes is the default.

