	  misspelling of dependencies

2004-01-30 21:11  robert

	* Make/dependancies, Make/makedirdefs: Added new dependancies file
	  which contains a list of libraries that various
	  OSG modules depend upon, these can be set as installed or not.
	  The makedirdefs
	  now uses this to configure which modules to compile.

