	* Make/makedefs: Added ARCH64 def for 64 bit builds

2002-10-17 21:25  don

	* Make/makedefs: USE_MM was not defined for IRIX

2002-10-17 13:48  robert

	* Make/debugtests.bat, Make/osgtests.bat: Renamed the
	  RenderBin::sort_local to sortImplementation(),
	  draw_local to drawImplementation() and added a new
	  RenderBin::DrawCallback().
	  
	  Added osgcubemap to the Make/ test scripts.

2002-10-10 12:44  robert

	* Make/makedirdefs: Added Macro's new cube map generation classes
	  and osgcubemap demo.

2002-10-08 07:39  don

	* Make/makerules: Added AnimationPathManipulator to osgGA and
	  modified sgv to use it.

2002-10-08 05:41  don

	* Make/makerules: Fixed some inconsistencies between header files
	  and function definitions
	  where the header file declared a parameter non-const, but the
	  function
	  definition expected a const. The Solaris linker was coming up
	  with
	  undefined symbols.

2002-10-07 21:23  robert

	* Make/debugtests.bat, Make/osgtests.bat: Added extra convinience
	  methods to LOD - addChild(child,min,max).
	  
	  Added osganimate to test scripts.

