	* Make/makedefs, Make/makerules: Oops forgot to add makedefs and
	  makerules

2002-04-02 06:44  don

	* Make/instrules, Make/instrules.new, Make/makedefs.cyg,
	  Make/makedefs.freebsd, Make/makedefs.irix.std,
	  Make/makedefs.irix.std.64, Make/makedefs.linux,
	  Make/makedefs.macosx, Make/makedefs.mingw, Make/makedefs.new,
	  Make/makerules.cyg, Make/makerules.freebsd, Make/makerules.irix,
	  Make/makerules.linux, Make/makerules.macosx,
	  Make/makerules.mingw, Make/makerules.new, Makefile: The new order
	  for building OSG. All Makefiles are replaced and
	  the Make directory is left with four files only :
	  makedefs
	  makerules
	  makedirrules
	  instrules
	  
	  These work for all platforms supported so far, which include :
	  Linux
	  Irix
	  Solaris
	  MacOSX
	  Cygwin
	  FreeBSD

